WEBVTT

00:00.679 --> 00:02.210
<i>Previously on
"The Vampire Diaries"...</i>

00:02.211 --> 00:05.580
Silas wants me to drop the veil
between our side and the other side.

00:05.580 --> 00:07.216
You will open
the floodgates

00:07.217 --> 00:08.699
for every supernatural being
that has ever died ?

00:08.700 --> 00:10.177
It's done. The veil is down.

00:10.478 --> 00:12.470
Hey.

00:12.471 --> 00:13.970
Who the hell is that?

00:13.972 --> 00:15.139
That is my ex-boyfriend Alexander.

00:15.140 --> 00:17.268
We should get out of here.

00:17.676 --> 00:20.010
You should...
Too bad you can't

00:20.012 --> 00:21.061
Silas?

00:21.063 --> 00:24.148
I can make you see
whatever I want you to see.

00:24.441 --> 00:27.485
You have no idea who I am.

00:27.486 --> 00:30.387
I will make your
body turn to stone.

00:30.388 --> 00:31.772
Isn't she your girlfriend?

00:31.773 --> 00:33.469
Who knows?
I know she was sired to me,

00:33.470 --> 00:34.609
I know her emotions were off.

00:34.610 --> 00:36.405
What the hell am I
supposed to do with this?

00:36.406 --> 00:37.445
Get the girl.

00:37.446 --> 00:39.646
I can bring Jeremy back.
I can keep him here!

00:39.648 --> 00:40.916
No, you can't.

00:41.082 --> 00:43.033
Phasmatos, raverus un animun.

00:45.453 --> 00:48.038
Oh, my God.
I'm dead.

