01:04.629 --> 01:06.650
Welcome back.

01:07.833 --> 01:11.434
It was our deaths that allowed
this day to come to pass,

01:11.436 --> 01:15.701
massacres performed in the name
of resurrecting the immortal Silas.

01:15.867 --> 01:19.093
12 hybrids, 12 witches,

01:19.094 --> 01:20.998
the slaughter of innocents
by the so-called

01:21.164 --> 01:24.848
hero protectors of Mystic Falls.

01:24.850 --> 01:26.967
They risked unleashing
hell on earth

01:26.968 --> 01:28.755
for their own selfish gains,

01:31.440 --> 01:33.635
and today...

01:33.801 --> 01:35.826
That's exactly what
they're going to get.

01:37.995 --> 01:43.827
